Investing with purpose
We generate investment income and grow the capital that allows Allstate to pay claims, develop innovative products and services, and maintain financial stability. By doing so, we support Allstate’s mission to protect customers from life’s uncertainties and prepare them for the future.
We take a dynamic and collaborative approach to investing, guided by three core principles:


Understand business needs to deliver strong investment results with an appropriate risk/return profile.

Maintain dynamic and forward-looking views on markets and emerging trends.

Continuously develop the expertise of our team and build a strong network of world-class partners.










