 Strategic allocation, dynamic risk

Our portfolio management begins with our global economic and market outlook, which informs a quantitative modeling process that balances risk and return, factoring in elements such as diversification, duration, liquidity and capital.
We overlay key global themes and trends and invite a variety of diverse perspectives as we make asset allocation decisions. Our portfolio managers then assess fundamentals, valuations and technical factors across markets to generate strong returns through the investment cycle.
















